replies.body:
Most of the time that Kernel issue can be fixed by making sure Windows has the right permissions set up to allow League to function correctly. Go through the steps in our [**permission guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/204134104-Setting-up-your-Permissions), and you should be able to get League working again.

Also, I think your English is coming along pretty well to be honest!!
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
